(Atho LMDB Storage Overview) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Date: 2026-04-09) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This document defines which LMDB stores are consensus-critical vs local/runtime) Tj
T*
(state, and why each store exists.) Tj
T*
(- Database Root) Tj
T*
(Root path:) Tj
T*
(- blockchain_storage/<network>/) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Configured in:) Tj
T*
(- Src/Utility/const.py \(Constants.DATABASES\)) Tj
T*
(- Store Classification) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Consensus-Critical Stores \(network state\)) Tj
T*
(These stores are replayed/validated from canonical blocks and directly affect) Tj
T*
(validation outcomes.) Tj
T*
(- full_block_chain*.lmdb) Tj
T*
(- Code: Src/Storage/blockstorage.py) Tj
T*
(- Role: canonical block bodies, tx location index, tip metadata.) Tj
T*
(- Consensus impact: highest.) Tj
T*
(- utxo*.lmdb) Tj
T*
(- Code: Src/Storage/utxostorage.py) Tj
T*
(- Role: spendable output set + apply/unspend markers.) Tj
T*
(- Consensus impact: highest.) Tj
T*
(- private_notes*.lmdb) Tj
T*
(- Code: Src/Storage/private_notes_store.py) Tj
T*
(- Role: shielded note set, nullifier sets, Merkle tree nodes, anchor roots.) Tj
T*
(- Consensus impact: highest for private tx validity.) Tj
T*
(- bond*.lmdb) Tj
T*
(- Code: Src/Storage/bondstake.py) Tj
T*
(- Role: bond lock state machine, miner eligibility linkage.) Tj
T*
(- Consensus impact: high \(bonded mining checks\).) Tj
T*
(- stake*.lmdb) Tj
T*
(- Code: Src/Storage/bondstake.py) Tj
T*
(- Role: stake lock state machine + network totals used by staking logic.) Tj
T*
(- Consensus impact: high \(staking constraints/rewards\).) Tj
T*
(- payout_journal*.lmdb) Tj
T*
(- Code: Src/Storage/bondstake.py) Tj
T*
(- Role: deterministic payout idempotency/event history.) Tj
T*
(- Consensus impact: high for safe replay/reorg payout behavior.) Tj
T*
(- Why it is required:) Tj
T*
(- prevents duplicate payouts across retries/restarts,) Tj
T*
(- preserves ordered payout transitions \(pending -> submitted -> confirmed\),) Tj
T*
(- enables deterministic reprocessing after crashes/reorg windows.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Local Runtime/Propagation Stores) Tj
T*
(Important for networking and performance, but not canonical chain truth.) Tj
T*
(- mempool*.lmdb) Tj
T*
(- Code: Src/Storage/mempool.py) Tj
T*
(- Role: pending tx propagation, fee/ranking indexes, tombstones.) Tj
T*
(- Canonical source remains accepted blocks, not mempool records.) Tj
T*
