(- orphan_blocks*.lmdb) Tj
T*
(- Code: Src/Blockchain/orphreorgs.py) Tj
T*
(- Role: orphan/side-branch staging for bounded reorg handling.) Tj
T*
(- Becomes canonical only when blocks are accepted into block store.) Tj
T*
(- Runtime Deletion/Recovery Expectations) Tj
T*
(- Deleting a consensus store while node is running is unsafe by default.) Tj
T*
(- Current hardening behavior:) Tj
T*
(- LMDB begin paths detect missing backing paths,) Tj
T*
(- affected stores attempt environment recovery/reopen,) Tj
T*
(- consensus code still treats missing/corrupt required state as validation) Tj
T*
(    failure rather than accepting uncertain state.) Tj
T*
(- Operational recommendation:) Tj
T*
(- stop node before manual DB deletion unless intentionally testing recovery.) Tj
T*
(- Map Growth / Rollover) Tj
T*
(Atho uses bounded LMDB map growth:) Tj
T*
(- on MapFullError, stores may grow map size \(if enabled\),) Tj
T*
(- growth is capped by per-store limits,) Tj
T*
(- near-limit pressure is logged.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Important:) Tj
T*
(- LMDB page reuse does not shrink map size automatically.) Tj
T*
(- pruning/cleanup frees pages for reuse but does not compact file size.) Tj
T*
(- Operational Checks) Tj
T*
(- Inspect store health:) Tj
T*
(- Watch logs for map pressure and recovery events.) Tj
T*
(- Increase max map size before sustained high-write load if near limits.) Tj
T*
(- Related Files) Tj
T*
(- Src/Storage/lmdbutils.py) Tj
T*
(- Src/Storage/blockstorage.py) Tj
T*
(- Src/Storage/utxostorage.py) Tj
T*
(- Src/Storage/private_notes_store.py) Tj
T*
(- Src/Storage/mempool.py) Tj
T*
(- Src/Storage/bondstake.py) Tj
T*
(- Src/Blockchain/orphreorgs.py) Tj
T*
(- Production Operating Guidance) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(For long-running production-like nodes, treat LMDB behavior as part of reliability engineering,) Tj
T*
(not just storage internals. Recommended baseline:) Tj
T*
(- monitor map usage growth trends, not only absolute map size,) Tj
T*
(- alert before LMDB_ROLLOVER_ALERT_THRESHOLD is reached,) Tj
T*
(- snapshot/backup before planned store maintenance,) Tj
T*
(- keep store path ownership and permissions explicit per deployment user.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(When migrating hosts, copy complete store sets together \(block, utxo, private_notes, bond,) Tj
T*
(stake, payout_journal\) so state-machine relationships remain consistent. Partial copies can) Tj
T*
(produce hard-to-debug replay inconsistencies.) Tj
T*
(- Policy Snapshot Context) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Storage behavior supports active policy constants but does not define them. Current production) Tj
T*
(policy references used by upper layers include:) Tj
T*
(- tx confirmations 10, private tx confirmations 10, coinbase maturity 150,) Tj
T*
(- fee floor 500 atoms/vB,) Tj
T*
ET
